  "name": "RPlog_A_Lady_Displeases_Her_Lord",
  "title": "A Lady Displeases Her Lord",
  "summary": "At a formal Imperial social gathering in an officers' lounge honoring the departed Admiral Adlerson, Minister Drocal Arconen holds court with the spymaster Director Joir, the scarred Chief Intelligence Officer Morganna Tazecks, and the young pilot Azya Aguilira. The conversation is a chilly contest of veiled power-plays as Drocal probes Morganna's loyalties and tests Azya, while Joir maneuvers to gauge the Minister's allegiances by invoking the New Order and the fate of Moff Rhys. When Morganna, chafing under the relentless status games, snaps that everyone should drop the posturing and simply have a drink, Drocal rounds on her with cold fury for her insolence and orders her to learn her place. Defeated but seething, Morganna excuses herself to cool off, snarling past the flirtatious Lieutenant Jolan as she leaves, while the ensign Bronwyn observes the whole scene with detached amusement. Sensing Joir knows something important, Drocal suggests they continue privately, and the two retire upstairs to the senior officers' tier to talk away from the crowd.",
